      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起: 2型糖尿病のβ細胞減少という臨床課題",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf}.main{flex:1;display:flex;padding:0 60px;gap:40px;align-items:center}.left-panel{flex:1}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:24px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px}.body-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.8;color:#e2e8f0}.alert-box{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);border-left:5px solid #14b8a6;padding:24px 30px;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;margin-top:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.4}</style><div class='slide'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>SLIDE 2/8</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='main'><div class='left-panel'><p class='section-label'>起 ── QUESTION</p><h2>β細胞が減り続ける問題</h2><p class='body-text'>2型糖尿病の発症時点で、膵β細胞量は<br>すでに健常者の<strong style=\"color:#2dd4bf\">約50%</strong>にまで減少しています。</p><div class='alert-box'><p>現在の治療薬はインスリン抵抗性の改善や<br>分泌促進が中心。<br><strong style=\"color:#2dd4bf\">β細胞そのものを「増やす」薬剤は存在しない。</strong></p></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
