      "title": "ChREBPとは何か",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承: ChREBPの基礎知識とアイソフォーム",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#0a1a1a;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{flex:1;display:flex;padding:0 60px;gap:40px;align-items:center}.left-panel{flex:1}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px}.card{background:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 30px;margin-bottom:16px}.card-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.point-box{border-left:5px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.05);padding:20px 28px;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;margin-top:16px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.4}</style><div class='slide'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>SLIDE 3/8</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='main'><div class='left-panel'><p class='section-label'>承 ── BACKGROUND</p><h2>ChREBPとは何か</h2><div class='card'><p class='card-title'>ChREBP&#945;（基本型）</p><p class='card-text'>構成的に発現。グルコース上昇で活性化し、ChREBPβの転写を誘導する。</p></div><div class='card'><p class='card-title'>ChREBP&#946;（活性型）</p><p class='card-text'>グルコース誘導性。強力な転写活性でβ細胞増殖を促進する。</p></div><div class='point-box'><p><strong>注意:</strong> ChREBPβの過剰発現はグルコトキシシティを誘導し、逆にβ細胞死を引き起こす（二面性）</p></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
