      "style": "dark",
      "content": "転: 膵β細胞特異的ChREBP欠損マウスの実験結果",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf}.main{flex:1;display:flex;padding:0 60px;align-items:center}.left-panel{flex:1}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:28px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#0f172a;background:#2dd4bf;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0}.list-result{color:#2dd4bf;font-weight:700}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.4}</style><div class='slide'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>SLIDE 4/8</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='main'><div class='left-panel'><p class='section-label'>転 ── NEW FINDINGS</p><h2>京都大学の新発見（2026年4月）</h2><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>1</span><p class='list-text'><strong>S961投与モデル</strong>（急性高血糖）<br><span class='list-result'>→ ChREBP欠損でβ細胞増殖が有意に抑制</span></p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>2</span><p class='list-text'><strong>高脂肪食モデル</strong>（慢性高血糖）<br><span class='list-result'>→ ChREBP欠損でβ細胞増殖が有意に抑制</span></p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>3</span><p class='list-text'><strong>妊娠モデル</strong>（生理的変化）<br><span class='list-result'>→ ChREBP欠損の影響は限定的</span></p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>4</span><p class='list-text'><strong>標的遺伝子Rgs16</strong>を新たに同定<br><span class='list-result'>→ 高血糖下でのみ発現誘導、増殖に関与</span></p></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
