      "style": "light",
      "content": "結: 臨床で意識すべきポイント",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#0a1a1a;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{flex:1;display:flex;padding:0 60px;align-items:center}.left-panel{flex:1}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:28px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;background:#0d4a4a;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.4}</style><div class='slide'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>SLIDE 5/8</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='main'><div class='left-panel'><p class='section-label'>結 ── CLINICAL IMPLICATION</p><h2>臨床への示唆</h2><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>1</span><p class='list-text'><strong>早期介入でβ細胞を守る</strong><br>HbA1c 8%を超える前に治療強化を</p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>2</span><p class='list-text'><strong>β細胞には増殖能がある</strong><br>条件次第で増えうる — 患者説明にも活用</p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>3</span><p class='list-text'><strong>β細胞保護を意識した薬剤選択</strong><br>GLP-1RA、TZDのエビデンスを整理</p></div><div class='list-item'><span class='list-num'>4</span><p class='list-text'><strong>ChREBP経路が将来の創薬標的</strong><br>内因性増殖 + 外因性補充の両面で進展</p></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
